						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying in a field about a furlong to the west of the village.</p>						

						<p>1524 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1445, Svabhānu, Māgha, ba. 30, Friday, corresponding to 1524 A.D., February 4. The weekday, however, was Thursday.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land to the god Siddhēśvara of Muḷugunda by Vemgaḷapa, son of Bāgila Malapa-nāyaka. </p>						

						</summary>
